BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260422T063000
DTEND:20260422T075400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.669ft at 06:30\n-0.065ft at 07:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Decent mix of WNW/NW swells and some S swell rolling in. Thigh-waist high 
 surf for average spots\, hitting shoulder high for select spots able to pu
 ll in the S swell on tap.\n\nAnother drained mid morning low tide to try w
 ork around. Light+ S winds then for some crumble.  Afternoon gets cleaner 
 as winds go offshore WNW for town spots.
END:VEVENT
