BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260423T063000
DTEND:20260423T091200
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.995ft at 06:30\n-0.065ft at 09:12\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Mix of WNW/NW swells and some S swell is slightly down from Wednesday\, bu
 t a new mid-period WNW will be on the rise through the back half of the da
 y. That pushes better spots back into the chest to shoulder high range in 
 the afternoon. Mind the mid day\, draining negative low tide. \n\nConditio
 ns are looking much better compared to previous days with light/variable w
 inds expected through the day. 
END:VEVENT
